      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, preserved in a state that mirrors its original showroom delivery. This vehicle features an unblemished exterior profile and a pristine interior, reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled storage. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that is both fluid and precise. For the discerning buyer who demands a vehicle of superlative caliber and investment-grade quality, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
